teal.physics.em

Interface GeneratesB

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Circuit, Coil, ConstantField, CurrentSlab, CylindricalMagnet, Dipole, ElectricDipole, EMRadiator, FiniteWire, GenericBField, HollowCurrentShell, InfiniteWire, LineMagneticDipole, MagneticDipole, RingOfCurrent, Seafloor

    public interface GeneratesB
    Objects that generate a magnetic field should implement GeneratesB. When a World responds to getB requests, it will only sum up the magnetic fields of GeneratesB objects.
